    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "orchestration_body",
      "x": 650,
      "y": 784,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 168,
      "text": "Comfort Management\n  Reads temp/humidity/air quality \u2192 compares vs. preferences\n  \u2192 adjusts climate, lighting, ventilation\n\nEnergy Monitoring\n  ha_get_statistics: daily/weekly consumption by device\n  Flags anomalies, tracks savings vs. baseline\n\nDevice Health Tracking\n  Scans states for offline/low-battery/error signals\n  Stores issues in memory (volatile, high importance)\n  Alerts on degraded devices before user notices",
      "originalText": "Comfort Management\n  Reads temp/humidity/air quality \u2192 compares vs. preferences\n  \u2192 adjusts climate, lighting, ventilation\n\nEnergy Monitoring\n  ha_get_statistics: daily/weekly consumption by device\n  Flags anomalies, tracks savings vs. baseline\n\nDevice Health Tracking\n  Scans states for offline/low-battery/error signals\n  Stores issues in memory (volatile, high importance)\n  Alerts on degraded devices before user notices",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
