    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "memory_body",
      "x": 1258,
      "y": 784,
      "width": 264,
      "height": 224,
      "text": "Stores:\n  comfort_preference (stable)\n  comfort_deviation (volatile)\n  energy_baseline (standard)\n  energy_spike (volatile)\n  energy_pattern (standard)\n  scene_preference (stable)\n  automation_schedule (standard)\n  device_issue (volatile)\n  usage_pattern (standard)\n\nRetrieves:\n  memory_search\n  memory_recall\n\nUsed for:\n  comparing readings vs.\n  stored preferences",
      "originalText": "Stores:\n  comfort_preference (stable)\n  comfort_deviation (volatile)\n  energy_baseline (standard)\n  energy_spike (volatile)\n  energy_pattern (standard)\n  scene_preference (stable)\n  automation_schedule (standard)\n  device_issue (volatile)\n  usage_pattern (standard)\n\nRetrieves:\n  memory_search\n  memory_recall\n\nUsed for:\n  comparing readings vs.\n  stored preferences",
